      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Approach 1 : nCr (number of combinations)\nFormula: nCr = n!/[r! (n-r)!]\nn : The total number of items in the set.\nr : The number of items to be chosen.\n! : Factorial symbol (e.g., 4! = 4 * 3 * 2 * 1).",
